OL,3,CLiving in a tent and in limbo: The
OL,4,Ctough reality for asylum seekers
OL,6,FYonas' story
OL,8,FFor four months, Yonas has lived on
OL,9,Fthe street in a showerproof tent.
OL,11,FHe is a refugee seeking asylum fleeing
OL,12,Fthe Civil War in Eritrea, an only
OL,13,Fchild.
OL,15,FThe 23-year-old arrived by a boat
OL,16,Fafter travelling through Libya and
OL,17,FItaly.
OL,19,FHis mother is somewhere in Sudan and
OL,20,Fhis father is a soldier.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
