OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772547084
OL,3,CLiving in a tent and in limbo: The
OL,4,Ctough reality for asylum seekers
OL,6,FHe says he doesn't want to show his
OL,7,Fface as he doesn't want his mother to
OL,8,Fsee the reality of his life in the UK.
OL,10,FWhen asked if he is happy or regrets
OL,11,Fleaving Eritrea, he says he's fifty-
OL,12,Ffifty.
OL,14,FAn Afghan refugee's story
OL,16,FIn another tent is a man from Kabul in
OL,17,FAfghanistan who says he has been
OL,18,Fhomeless on the streets of Manchester
OL,19,Ffor three years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
