FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772547084
OL,3,CLiving in a tent and in limbo: The
OL,4,Ctough reality for asylum seekers
OL,6,FHe is seeking asylum, and wants to
OL,7,Fwork, but says he simply survives here
OL,8,Fin the freezing conditions through the
OL,9,Fkindness of strangers.
OL,11,FIn 2017, when Andy Burnham was
OL,12,Felected, Greater Manchester Mayor, he
OL,13,Fpromised to end rough sleeping by 2020.
OL,15,FHe pledged a bed every night, which
OL,16,Fincludes support for refugees.
OL,18,FBut six years on, that target remains,
OL,19,Fand he blames Home Office and the
OL,20,FTreasury, forcing more people on the
OL,21,Fstreets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
