CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772547084
OL,3,CLiving in a tent and in limbo: The
OL,4,Ctough reality for asylum seekers
OL,6,FMr Burnham said: "I'm going be honest
OL,7,Fand say, the task that we have faced
OL,8,Fhas not been made any easier by the
OL,9,Factions of the Home Office in recent
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,12,FThey pose as tough on benefits, and,
OL,13,Fyou know, let's freeze local housing
OL,14,Fallowance. What I've seen in my role,
OL,15,Fwhen those decisions are taken, it
OL,16,Fjust builds the number of families who
OL,17,Fpresent as homeless."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
