OL,3,CLiving in a tent and in limbo: The
OL,4,Ctough reality for asylum seekers
OL,6,FYanas like the others in tents, lives
OL,7,Fon a hot meal a day from a local
OL,8,Fcharity, and they wash where they can.
OL,9,FAnd then they wait to see if asylum
OL,10,Fstatus is granted, and they can make
OL,11,Fthe northwest their home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
